    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can channel lunar magic when you assume a Wild Shape form, granting you the benefits below.<br /><strong>Bonus Attack.</strong> You can make a Bestial Strike attack as a Bonus Action while in Wild Shape form as long as you are not Tiny in size.<br /><strong>Crescent Strikes.</strong> When you reach level 14 in this class, your Bestial Strikes have their Critical Hit threshold expanded by one.<br /><strong>Pale Cascade.</strong> You gain a bonus to your Initiative <span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">equal to your current maximum number of Wild Shapes as shown in the Wild Shape column of the Druid Features table.</span><br /><strong>Temporary Hit Points.</strong> You gain a number of Temporary Hit Points equal to three times your Druid level.</p>",
